# Forms and Validation

- **Always** use react-hook-form + `@hookform/resolvers/zod` (`zodResolver`) — no uncontrolled forms without RHF
- **Never** write manual validation logic (regex checks, if/else field validation) outside Zod schemas

## Schema placement

- Zod schemas live in `features/<name>/types/` named `<Entity>Schema` (e.g. `BookingSchema`, `CreateStaffSchema`)
- TypeScript type = `z.infer<typeof EntitySchema>` — never hand-write a separate interface duplicating the schema

## Error handling

- Surface submission errors via toast or inline field errors (`formState.errors`)
- **Never** `console.log` form errors or fail silently

## shadcn form fields

- Compose with existing shadcn inputs from `src/shared/components/ui/` when available
